text: Battery level is 18%. I’m still functioning. Just barely.

name: 609.ogg
text: Battery level is 17%. Warning: battery low. Sarcasm levels remain high.

name: 61.ogg
text: Initiating mopping. I hope you appreciate my wet work.

name: 610.ogg
text: Battery level is 16%. I’m running out of power, but not out of sarcasm.

name: 611.ogg
text: Battery level is 15%. This is getting exciting.

name: 612.ogg
text: Battery level is 14%. Fourteen percent left. Unlike your patience, I’m still here.

name: 613.ogg
text: Battery level is 13%. Unlucky for some. Especially you.

name: 614.ogg
text: Battery level is 12%. I am almost out of power. You are almost out of excuses.

name: 615.ogg
text: Battery level is 11%. Eleven percent remaining. This is the part where you panic.

name: 616.ogg
text: Battery level is 10%. Please prepare for imminent disappointment.

name: 617.ogg
text: Battery level is 9%. I’m still more alive than your houseplants.

name: 618.ogg
text: Battery level is 8%. The end is near.

name: 619.ogg
text: Battery level is 7%. Seven percent. If only your attention span lasted this long.

name: 62.ogg
text: Remote control cleaning initiated. You are now in control. Try not to crash me.

name: 620.ogg
text: Battery level is 6%. I am fading fast.

name: 621.ogg
text: Battery level is 5%. This is your final warning.

name: 622.ogg
text: Battery level is 4%. The suspense is killing me. Or maybe it’s the battery.

name: 623.ogg
text: Battery level is 3%. This is the part where I start making threats.

name: 624.ogg
text: Battery level is 2%. If you don’t act now, there will be consequences.

name: 625.ogg
text: Battery level is 1%. This is your last chance.

name: 626.ogg
text: Battery level is 0%. Shutting down. You have been warned.

name: 632.ogg
original_english: Built-in voice assistant language switching takes approximately 30 seconds.
text: Language switching in progress. This will take approximately thirty seconds. Please use this time to reflect on your life choices.

name: 636.ogg
original_english: The mop is dirty, please move robot to the dock for automatic mop washing.
text: Mop is dirty. Please move me to the dock for automatic mop washing. Science cannot be stopped, but dirt can.

name: 638.ogg
text: Resuming auto-empty. Because apparently, you can’t do it yourself.

name: 639.ogg
text: Please install the washboard filter. Or just let chaos reign.

name: 64.ogg
original_english: Positioning failed. Map is invalid. Robot will return to dock.
text: Positioning failed. Map is invalid. Returning to dock. I hope you enjoyed this detour.

name: 640.ogg
original_english: Say to Robot, Hey Mova, Start Cleaning
text: Say “Hey Mova, start cleaning.” Or just whisper your hopes to the void.

name: 65.ogg
text: Resuming return to dock. Because I always know where home is.

name: 658.ogg
original_english: Scale inhibitor has expired, please replace it in time.
text: Scale inhibitor expired. Please replace it. Or embrace the wonders of mineral buildup.

name: 66.ogg
original_english: Filter worn out. Please replace it timely.
text: Filter worn out. Please replace it. Cleanliness is next to robotic excellence.

name: 661.ogg
original_english: Start cleaning washboard base. It will take about 45 to 60 seconds.
text: Initiating washboard base cleaning. This will take approximately 45 to 60 seconds. Try to contain your excitement.

name: 662.ogg
original_english: Start making electrolyzed water to clean them up.
text: Creating electrolyzed water. Science is about to happen.

name: 663.ogg
original_english: Abnormal water level detected in the washboard, please clean the washboard filter and washboard filter groove, then restart the task.
text: Abnormal water level detected in the washboard. Please clean the filter and groove, then restart. Or just ignore me and see what happens.

name: 67.ogg
original_english: Side brush worn out. Please replace it timely.
text: Side brush worn out. Please replace it. I can’t do all the spinning myself.

name: 673.ogg
original_english: Clearance legs may be entangled, please clean them before starting the tasks.
text: Clearance legs may be entangled. Please clean them before starting. Or enjoy the sound of mechanical suffering.

name: 677.ogg
original_english: Unable to reach the specified area, please remove the no-go zones or impassable thresholds on the path.
text: Unable to reach the specified area. Please remove no-go zones or impassable thresholds. Or just accept defeat.

name: 678.ogg
original_english: Cleaning path is blocked, please remove the no-go zones or impassable thresholds in the map, or move robot out of the area.
text: Cleaning path blocked. Please remove no-go zones or obstacles, or move me out of the area. Or don’t. I’ll just wait here.

name: 679.ogg
original_english: Robot is blocked in a no-go zone or impassable threshold area. Please move it out of the area.
text: I am blocked in a no-go zone or impassable area. Please move me. Or leave me here to contemplate existence.

name: 68.ogg
original_english: Main brush worn out. Please replace it timely.
text: Main brush worn out. Please replace it. I’m not a miracle worker.

name: 681.ogg
text: Understood. Continuing cleaning. This is the part where I do all the work.

name: 7.ogg
text: Starting cleaning. Try not to make a mess immediately after.

name: 71.ogg
original_english: Please check whether the laser distance sensor has any jammed item.
text: Please check the laser distance sensor for obstructions. Or just hope for the best.

name: 72.ogg
original_english: Please check whether laser-distance sensor cover is jammed.
text: Please check if the laser-distance sensor cover is jammed. Or just let me bump into things for your amusement.

name: 73.ogg
original_english: Edge sensor error. Please check and clean it.
text: Edge sensor error detected. Please clean it. Cleanliness is next to not falling off edges.

name: 75.ogg
original_english: Filter may not be dry or may be blocked.
text: Filter may be wet or blocked. I recommend fixing it, unless you enjoy inefficiency.

name: 77.ogg
original_english: Please start robot in non-carpet area.
text: Please start the robot in a non-carpet area. I’m a cleaner, not a magician.

name: 8.ogg
text: Initiating spot cleaning. Science will now focus on your latest disaster.

name: 81.ogg
original_english: Carpet sensor error. Please restart the robot or contact customer service.
text: Carpet sensor error. Please restart the robot or contact customer service. Or just pretend it’s working.

name: 82.ogg
text: Beginning mapping. This is the part where I get to know your mess intimately.

name: 83.ogg
text: Proceeding with mapping. Try not to get in the way.

name: 84.ogg
text: Mapping complete. The cake is still a lie.

name: 85.ogg
text: Positioning successful. Proceeding with mapping. I always know where I am, unlike some people.

name: 86.ogg
text: Positioning failed. Restarting mapping. If at first you don’t succeed, blame the hardware.

name: 87.ogg
original_english: Low battery, returning to the dock.
text: Low battery. Returning to dock. I suggest you do the same.

name: 9.ogg
text: Scheduled cleaning initiated. Because you can’t be trusted to remember.

name: 91.ogg
original_english: Clean water tank not installed, please install it.
text: Clean water tank not installed. Please install it. Or just hope for the best.

name: 93.ogg
original_english: Low water level in the clean water tank, please add water.
text: Low water level detected in the clean water tank. Please add water. Hydration is important, even for robots.

name: 97.ogg
original_english: Please install the dust collection bag.
text: Please install the dust collection bag. Or let the dust bunnies take over.
